txt.en: You have assisted the Woodcutter's Brotherhood in their efforts throughout the Wildwood of Bree-land. All those in the Brotherhood are thankful for your aid.
The Woodcutter's Brotherhood is in need of assistance with efforts in the Wildwood of Bree-land.
Complete factionless quests in the Wildwood to assist the Woodcutter's Brotherhood.

'The success of the Woodcutter's Brotherhood is determined by each of its members, and we can ill-afford to be unprepared when the village of Trestlebridge depends upon us.'\n\n'Aid the Woodcutter's Brotherhood in our tasks, and I shall see that your efforts are rewarded.'
